  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2015-06-17",
    "date": "2015-07-08T17:43:12Z",
    "text": "Sunshine on Government Act of 2015\n\nRequires the Office of Management and Budget (OMB) to create a separate website with a distinct URL, apart from the OMB website,\u00a0about the reports issued by each Office of Inspector General. Requires such website to include: (1) a general description of the role of the\u00a0Office of Inspector General, (2) a description of the types of reports issued by the Office of Inspector General, (3) a list of each federal agency that has an Office of Inspector General, and (4) a link to a website containing Inspector General reports."
  },
